{"title":"🦄TypeScript入门","uid":"877c463946b5e9a689020267f93becc8","slug":"typescript/typescript入门","date":"2020-01-09T00:30:20.000Z","updated":"2024-05-09T15:55:21.985Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/typescript/typescript入门.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"简介\"><a href=\"#简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"简介\"></a>简介</h2><p><img src=\"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/blog-img/TypeScript%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/Snipaste_2020-04-19_20-31-20.png\"><br>从 npm 包的下载量就可以看出 TypeScript 已经逐渐成为前端必不可少的工具了，都2020年了，再不学，就只能2021年学了🤣</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"/typescript/typescript%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8\">🦄TypeScript 入门</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Base\"><a href=\"#Base\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Base\"></a>Base</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"/typescript/typescript-webpack\">🌈TypeScript + Webpack</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/typescript/typescript%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\">🌈TypeScript 基础类型</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Web-Bookmark\"><a href=\"#Web-Bookmark\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Web Bookmark\"></a>Web Bookmark</h2><p><a href=\"https://github.com/KongValley/ToLearnTypeScript/tree/master/types\">GitHub仓库：基础类型</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Your-Environment\"><a href=\"#Your-Environment\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Your Environment\"></a>Your Environment</h2><p><strong>💡你需要做的准备：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Node.js &gt; 8.0，最好是最新的稳定版</li>\n<li>一个包管理工具 npm 或者 yarn</li>\n<li>一个文本编辑器或者 IDE</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Install-TypeScript\"><a href=\"#Install-TypeScript\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Install TypeScript\"></a>Install TypeScript</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install TypeScript -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Init-Project\"><a href=\"#Init-Project\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Init Project\"></a>Init Project</h2><p>先创建下目录</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> ts-study &amp;&amp; <span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> ts-study</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>再创建 src 目录（一般用来存放项目代码）</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> src &amp;&amp; <span class=\"built_in\">touch</span> src/index.ts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>注意：</strong> 如果你的系统是Windows的话，<code>touch</code>并不会生效，你可以用<code>New-Item</code>来代替<code>touch</code>，<a href=\"https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/issues/8621\">查看相关issue</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">New-Alias <span class=\"built_in\">touch</span> New-Item</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>初始化项目 package.json</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>初始化 ts 配置文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">tsc --init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"VSCode-Auto-Compile\"><a href=\"#VSCode-Auto-Compile\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"VSCode Auto Compile\"></a>VSCode Auto Compile</h2><p>在终端下拉菜单中选择运行任务</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/blog-img/TypeScript%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/ts-1.png\"></p>\n<p>选择<code>tsc:监视</code>（当你的文件发生改动时会自动编译）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/blog-img/TypeScript%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/ts-2.png\"></p>\n","text":"简介从 npm 包的下载量就可以看出 TypeScript 已经逐渐成为前端必不可少的工具了，都2020年了，再不学，就只能2021年学了🤣 Quick Sta...","permalink":"/post/typescript/typescript入门","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":642,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"TypeScript","slug":"TypeScript","count":4,"path":"api/categories/TypeScript.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"TypeScript Basic","slug":"TypeScript-Basic","count":4,"path":"api/tags/TypeScript-Basic.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">简介</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Quick-Start\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Quick Start</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Base\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Base</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Web-Bookmark\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Web Bookmark</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Your-Environment\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Your Environment</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Install-TypeScript\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Install TypeScript</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Init-Project\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Init Project</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#VSCode-Auto-Compile\"><span class=\"toc-text\">VSCode Auto Compile</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"大鹏","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/blog-img/avator/567.png","link":"/","description":"Web Developer","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/KongValley","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn